    notes: [
        "Phase 52c canonical pack for the starter farm coastal peninsula.",
        "The generator emits semantic terrain; this pack chooses season-aware concrete tiles and physical behavior.",
        "Autotile/transition bake still owns edges, shore foam masks, and water-depth transitions after this resolver pass.",
        "Placeholder tile ids are allowed so atlas expansion can follow without changing the resolver contract.",
    ],
